<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>{{ message.getSubject() }}</title>
</head>
<body>

<p>Dear <strong>{{ user.firstName ~ ' ' ~ user.lastName }}</strong>,</p>

<p>We received a password reset request for your account at {{ serverUrl() }}.</p>

<p>To reset your password, please visit the URL below:</p>

<a href="{{ url_password_reset }}">{{ url_password_reset }}</a>

<p>The above link becomes invalid after a successful login attempt.</p>

<p>If you did not request resetting your password, please disregard this
message and your password will remain unchanged.</p>

<p>Thank you</p>

</body>
</html>
